### BarberFlow API — IntelliJ HTTP Client
### Variáveis: defina em http-client.env.json ou substitua manualmente

# @no-redirect

### ============================================================
### VARIÁVEIS (edite aqui ou crie http-client.env.json)
### ============================================================
# baseUrl  = http://localhost:8080
# token    = <accessToken retornado no login>
# tenantId = <UUID do tenant>


### ============================================================
### TENANT & AUTH
### ============================================================

### 1. Criar tenant (cria admin automaticamente)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "barbearia-silva",
  "name": "Barbearia Silva",
  "adminEmail": "admin@silva.com",
  "adminPassword": "senha1234"
}

### ============================================================

### 2. Login
# > {%
#   client.global.set("token", response.body.accessToken);
#   client.global.set("tenantId", response.body.tenantId);
# %}
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@silva.com",
  "password": "senha1234"
}

### ============================================================
### CLIENTES
### ============================================================

### 3. Criar cliente
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "phone": "+5511999990001",
  "name": "João da Silva",
  "consentGiven": true
}

### ============================================================

### 4. Listar clientes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================================

### 5. Buscar cliente por telefone
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers/by-phone?phone=%2B5511999990001
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================================
### PROFISSIONAIS
### ============================================================

### 6. Criar profissional
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/professionals
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "Carlos Barbeiro",
  "specialties": ["Corte", "Barba", "Coloração"]
}

### ============================================================

### 7. Listar profissionais
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/professionals
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================================
### SERVIÇOS
### ============================================================

### 8. Criar serviço
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/services
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "Corte masculino",
  "price": 35.00,
  "durationMinutes": 30
}

### ============================================================

### 9. Criar serviço — Barba
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/services
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "name": "Barba",
  "price": 25.00,
  "durationMinutes": 20
}

### ============================================================

### 10. Listar serviços
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/services
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================================
### AGENDAMENTOS
### ============================================================

### 11. Criar agendamento
# Substitua customerId, professionalId e serviceIds pelos IDs reais
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "customerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "professionalId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "serviceIds": ["00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003"],
  "startAt": "2026-03-20T10:00:00-03:00"
}

### ============================================================

### 12. Listar agendamentos por intervalo de data
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments?from=2026-03-20T00:00:00Z&to=2026-03-20T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================================

### 13. Completar agendamento
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================================

### 14. Cancelar agendamento
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments/{{appointmentId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "reason": "Cliente solicitou cancelamento"
}

### ============================================================
### BILLING
### ============================================================

### 15. Iniciar trial
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/trial
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================================

### 16. Consultar assinatura
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================================

### 17. Ativar plano pago
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/billing/activate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "planTier": "GROWTH",
  "externalPaymentId": "pay_abc123"
}

### ============================================================
### CHATBOT (WhatsApp Webhook)
### ============================================================

### 18. Webhook WhatsApp — simular mensagem recebida
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/webhooks/whatsapp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "object": "whatsapp_business_account",
  "entry": [{
    "changes": [{
      "value": {
        "messages": [{
          "from": "5511999990001",
          "type": "text",
          "text": { "body": "Oi, quero agendar" }
        }],
        "metadata": { "phone_number_id": "{{tenantId}}" }
      }
    }]
  }]
}

### ============================================================
### HEALTH CHECK
### ============================================================

### 19. Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health
